{"tid":1357630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[街頭文鬥App] 招整合 警察濫權實錄／721上環元朗時序表","createTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T12:00:31.000Z","uid":112094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8c2e5ece777858873b6f1ebc89d1a49db9763b","tid":1357630,"uid":112094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"話說星期日行行下有個淨係睇CCTVB嘅人嚟挑機，去咗平行時空咁，又話示威者暴力打狗在先，又話警察好慘<br />\n<br />\n一時間想反駁揾片比佢睇，但一時間上網啲片同圖又好亂，一個月前612啲片又開始沉哂底。<br />\n<br />\n參考咗香城online <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1321785/page/1?post=d97ee51c92bc80f23704d054c708e2579828a797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1321785/page/1?post=d97ee51c92bc80f23704d054c708e2579828a797</a><br />\n<br />\n用Template整咗個簡單Web App，唔使裝，好似呢個咁：<a href=\"https://hkonline.glideapp.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkonline.glideapp.io%2F&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=de70c842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkonline.glideapp.io/</a><br />\nEdit Google Sheet 就可以update 資料，仲可以砌時序表，出街有人挑機可以即刻開link開片等佢無聲出<br />\n<br />\n入group放低Google account討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/BwXunhOhusr2J0GW3131Jg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FBwXunhOhusr2J0GW3131Jg&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=e2581c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/BwXunhOhusr2J0GW3131Jg</a><br />\n<br />\nDEMO<br />\n<a href=\"https://whatpopodid.glideapp.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhatpopodid.glideapp.io&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=23a8b1b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://whatpopodid.glideapp.io</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FofY09g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFofY09g.png&h=4c0878b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjD0u2D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjD0u2D.png&h=c8104475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1cP7Ph.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1cP7Ph.png&h=698b5220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWdLF9h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWdLF9h.png&h=9b6f9bb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33cd6dc4dff66ba5a90fea8925521c7143fa5852","tid":1357630,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:19:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f7b1bda97e338147de396f5afe647ced9fba6439","tid":1357630,"uid":264427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193ca28f5bf99e4b6c0777ec10610d828a9c3a63","tid":1357630,"uid":74572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:32:01.000Z","msg":"借位 順手幫推 麻煩幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【越洋幫拖】喺美國嘅香港人想收集警暴證據交畀美國警察同議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1358473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1358473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8d4b3ebf43c126944572158b6f4686f32f373ec1","tid":13